snippet.title: GOAT LEG FEET | Cooking & Eating in Village | Healthy Goat Leg Recipe | Traditional Mutton Recipes
snippet.description:
For this recipe, we used 100 goat leg feet. Goat legs contain bone, skin, and hair, so we cleaned them with hot water. After cleaning, we boiled the mutton leg feet, and finally, we cooked them with our traditional method. 
Usually, goat leg feet are used for mutton paya or bone soup, but we cook it as gravy. We enjoy this recipe on a rainy evening.

snippet.description:
#breakingnews #hindinews 
Maharashtra Bandh News : महाराष्‍ट्र के ठाणे जिले में
स्थित बदलापुर में स्‍कूल में बच्चियों से यौन उत्‍पीड़न के बाद फैली
हिंसा पर अब राज्‍य में राजनीति भी जमकर होने लगी है. शिवसेना (यूबीटी)
के चीफ उद्धव ठाकरे ने गुरुवार को इस घटना के विरोधी में 24 अगस्त को
महाराष्ट्र बंद का ऐलान किया है. सीएम एकनाथ शिंदे की सरकार इस बात की
जांच कर रही है कि कहीं ये हिंसा प्रायोजित तो नहीं थी. इसपर तीखा प्रहार
करते हुए उद्धव ने कहा कि यह घटना राजनीति से प्रेरित नहीं है बल्कि
महिलाओं और बच्चियों के खिलाफ अपराधों के लिए कड़ी सजा सुनिश्चित करने के
लिए एकता का आह्वान है.

snippet.title: Ibbani Tabbida lleyali Trailer | Vihan, Ankita, Mayuri | Chandrajith Belliappa | Paramvah Studios
snippet.description:
IBBANI TABBIDA ILEYALI is a beautifully crafted musical romance drama that tells the love story of Siddharth and Anahita. Narrated through a palette of colors, visual poetry, and refreshing music, it captures the essence of love through different phases of life and its varying shades. Come, fall in love all over again, and experience the magic of love.

snippet.title: Every Sister Ever | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys
This video shows crazy side of sisters when they are around each other. We love and annoy each other at the same time. It is always Badi Behan vs Choti Behan but it is also Behan Behan ka pyaar. They fight for no reason, sometimes the elder sister wins and vice versa. First child always has to go through family restrictions whereas things are always easier for the younger one , like getting married the pressure of a good idle for younger sister .  Raksha Bandhan celebration with siblings . This is a very comic and relatable video.  Every Behen Shopping fancy rakhi, getting mehendi done girls Favourite Henna, buying new ethnic dress , trying on sharara, anarkali suits, baiting brother for gifts by being sweet, giving him trendy rakhis. Middle class rakshabandhan, school Rakhi celebration and so much more . Every sister ever can relate with this video .
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family especially mom , sisters , brothers , cousins .. Comment down your Fav Part, 

Happy Raksha Bandhan 2024

Lyrics : 
Mere susar ke darwaje pe 
Moter car khadi se ri heeee 
X2

Here chandan ki si khusboo aave 
Mehak thave pure angan mein ji
Kom vom sab hold pe dharke
Tere pache aave hai ji

Hoor voor mane ghani ye tohli
Bargi tere paayi na re
Dharke sir pe jeghaad chori
Jada tu itrave na

Re descent banke aaja chore 
Yaar fajeete paave na
Mai haryana ka desi ragde
Faltu ke mane bhave na

Mai moter car pe latta maaru
Tik ke bhitar baith ja ne 
Mera baapu badya maanas 
Tere kede hai sasur ji 

Mere susar ke darwaje pe 
Moter car khadi se ri heeee
X2

Re gel mere tu chalde chori
Tanne puro gom ghumadu
Maa meri chulhe pe baithi
Garam garam tane saag khavadu

Bhaat purono baitho 
Waki copy mein tero nom chhadadu 
Sohna ke toku laau kundal
Palwal te paajeb dua du

Bhid bhaad no chale gel mein
Kuch ginti ke yaar 
paina ke rakhu tez kataar re
Meri bhot no talwar
Re jab jab ade garaari yaar ki 
Fir kond kare aarpaar
Thame hath re jinke dil te
Unku jon den ne tyar 

Re chora

Na paar basave chore 
Tere dhare rehjange tore
Jaldi manas banja jaan meri
Re din rehge se thode

Chore gurjar ke mai teri su
 Bas filkar vikar na kariye
Je gel mere rehna asle ka
Jikar vikar na kariye

Chora badda shikari
Ar mai chori su kawari
Meri gel ki sehli hase mere pe
Fasgi kit bechari

Mere yaar ki roj garaari
Mere pe aake adi se ri hee

Mere susar ke darwaje pe 
Moter car khadi se ri heeee
X2

Kaffara Episode 26 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nestlé Nangrow - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 22nd August 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Kaffara Digitally Presented by Nestlé Nangrow

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Episode 4170: Abdul Ki Waapsi
--------------------------------------------------------
Everyone is expecting Inspector Pandey to find Abdul and bring him back. However, Pandey Ji is coming back empty-handed and Abdul is nowhere to be found. Will he return?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Deepak Wadhwa is a well known options trader who has featured in Josh talks and talks extensively about stock market behaviour,has given several interviews on how to be a pro trader and also runs a series called deeptalks. His podcasts help not just to find right market directions but also how to make money using mutual funds,how beginners should invest and a lot more.
-
Time Stamps
- *00:00 - Introduction*
- *00:15 - A Trader Earns All Day but Loses Everything to the Market in the End*

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | રાકેશ બારોટ | Reshma Thakor | રેશ્મા ઠાકોર | સોના રૂપનિ ભમ્મર વેલ | ગુજરાતી ગીત 2024
snippet.description:
સાંભળો રાકેશ બારોટ અને રેશ્મા ઠાકોરનું નવું  ગીત સોના રૂપાણી ભમ્મર વહેલ ફક્ત @SaregamaGujarati પર

Listen to Rakesh Barot and Reshma Thakor's new happy song "Sona Roopani Bhammar Vehl" only on @SaregamaGujarati 

Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot, Reshma Thakor 
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema 
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Sweat  sen , Divya Rajani ,kirtiy kashiya 
Concept: Savya Bhati , Bhavesh Gorsiya
Director: Bhavesh Gorasiya
Creative Head: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya
Production Manager: Ramesh Halol 
Lyrics: Chandu Raval
Music: Rakesh Barot, Mehul Barot
Dop: Anu Patel ( viral )
choreographer Dipak turi 
Editor: Anu Patel ( viral )
Makeup & Hair : chirag parmar, mandakini                            
Rakesh Barot Costume: Manisha R Barot
Recoding: Dhoon Digital Recoding Studio Adalaj
lokeshan Richiya gaam ( Halol )

Lyrics:
હે હાવ હોના ની હે એવી રૂપા ની
હે હાવ હોના રે રૂપા ની ભમ્મર વેલ
વેલડીએ ઘમકે છે જેણી ગુગર માણા રાજ
હે જોડો પરણિયા જોડો ભમ્મર વેલ
કોનુંડો આયો ને મૈયર જાવું માણા રાજ
હે ચાર પાંચ દાડા થી મને એ બધી ખબર છે
તારા રે પિયર સોમે તારી રે નજર છે
હે લોમી લોમી છે હે ઘણી છેટી
હે લોમી લોમી છે તારા મૈયરયા ની વાટ
ઘૂઘરા રે ધમકાવી વેલડું છોડું માણા રાજ
હે કોનુંડો આયો ને મૈયર જાવું માણા રાજ
હે વ્હલી મારી મૈયર જઇ ને તમે મોરે થઇ રમજો
મોરે થઈને રમશો તો અમને બહુ ગમશો
ઓ ભવો ભવ ભરથાર થઇ ને મળજો
તમારા પહેલા પિયુ મોત મને આવજો
ઓ પિયુ તમે બોલો વાત મા તહેવારે
નથી રોકી જતી પિયર જાત મને તહેવારે
હે હું ચંપો ને (૩) તમે છો મારી કેળ
કોનુંડો રમી ને રાજી રેજો મારા રાજ
કોનુંડો આયો ને મૈયર જાવું માણા  રાજ
હો આયો કોનુંડો પિયુ હૈયે હરખ છે હેંડો અવે મોડું રે થાય છે
હો તારું પિયર ને ગોડી મારું છે સાસરું
ચિંતા ના કરો વેલડું જશે રે પોચડું
હે મારી ગોથેનો ભેગી રે થઇ છે વટિયો મારી જોઈ બેઠી છે
હે ઉગિયો ઉગિયો રે (2)
હે ઉગિયો ઉગિયો રે, સોમે પિયેરે પ્રારભત
દાડો આથમતા પહોંચી જાસુ રે મારા રાજ
હે આવે કોનુંડો રમી રાજી થશુ મારા રાજ
હે આવે કોનુંડો રમી રાજી રેજો મારા રાજ

#reshmathakor 
#saregamagujarati 
#gujaratisongs   
#gujaratilovesong

#ગુજરાતીગીત

snippet.title: Tikki Chole Recipe | Crispy Aloo Tikki Chaat | कुरकुरी चोले टिक्की | Chef Sanjyot Keer
snippet.description:
Full written recipe of Tikki Chole
Prep time: 20-25 mins (8-10 hrs soaking)
Cooking time: 1 hour 
Serves: 4-5 people
Chole
Ingredients:
CHICKPEA | काबुली चने 250 GRAMS
SALT | नमक TO TASTE
BLACK CARDAMOM | बड़ी इलायची 1 NO. 
BAY LEAF | तेज पत्ता 2 NOS. 
CLOVES | लौंग 4-5 NOS. 
BAKING SODA | बेकिंग सोडा A LARGE PINCH
WATER | पानी AS REQUIRED (1 INCH ABOVE CHICKPEAS)
GREEN CHILLI | हरी मिर्च 2 NOS. 
GINGER | अदरक 2 INCH
SALT | नमक A PINCH
GHEE | घी 2 TBSP
CUMIN SEEDS | जीरा A LARGE PINCH
ASAFOETIDA | हींग 1/4 TSP
SALT | नमक TO TASTE
BLACK SALT | काला नमक 1 TSP
SPICY RED CHILLI POWDER | तीखी लाल मिर्च पाउडर 2 TSP
YELLOW CHILLI POWDER | पीली मिर्च का पाउडर 2 TSP
CORIANDER POWDER | धनिया पाउडर 1 TBSP
GARAM MASALA | गरम मसाला 1 TSP
TAMARIND | इमली LEMON SIZED BALL (SOAKED)
GINGER | अदरक 1 INCH (JULIENNE)
ROASTED KASURI METHI POWDER | भुनी कसूरी मेथी का पाउडर A LARGE PINCH 
FRESH CORIANDER | हरा धनिया A HANDFUL (CHOPPED)
 Method:
Wash the chickpeas & soak then in water overnight or for 8-10 hours.
Discard the water & add the soaked chickpeas into a pressure cooker along with salt, whole spices, baking soda & water. 
Pressure cooker the chickpeas over high flame for the first whistle then cook for 4-5 more whistles over medium flame. 
Switch off the flame & let the cooker depressurize naturally. 
Make the ginger chilli paste by pounding them using a mortar pestle or a small mixer grinder. 
Set a kadhai over high flame, add the ghee & let it get hot. 
Further add cumin seeds, asafoetida & the paste, stir well & cook over high flame for a minute. 
Add the cooked chickpeas followed by all the powdered spices & tamarind water, stir well & cook over high flame for 7-8 minutes.
Mash a few chickpeas while stirring, this will help the chole to thicken up, the final consistency should be semi-thick but pourable. 
Lastly taste & adjust salt if required & add ginger, kasuri methi & fresh coriander, stir well. 
Your delicious chole are ready. 

Aloo Tikki
Ingredients:
POTATO | आलू 7-8 NOS. (BOILED)
SALT | नमक TO TASTE
CORN FLOUR | कॉर्न फ्लोर 3-4 TBSP
CORN FLOUR | कॉर्न फ्लोर AS REQUIRED 
GHEE | घी 3 TBSP
Method:
Grate & add the boiled potatoes in a large bowl then add salt & gradually add corn flour.
For the perfect tikki make sure you are using pahadi / indori / chipsona variety of potatoes or else the tikkis won’t turn out to be crispy. 
Mix well to combine & form a potato dough, the quantity of corn flour might vary depending on the quality of the potatoes, the mixture should not not be sticky it should just bind well. 
Take a small portion from the mixture of about 80-90 grams & from it into a roundel, then slightly press it to form a thick tikki then dust a few pinches of corn flour on it to coat it slightly, shape all the tikkis similarly. 
Set a large, flat pan over high flame & add ghee, let the ghee get moderately hot. 
Place the tikkis & fry them over medium flame until they turn light golden brown from both the sides. 
Then using a potato masher, mash the tikkis to form thick discs then fry the tikkis over medium low flame until they turn golden brown & crisp from both the sides. 
Your super crispy aloo tikkis are ready. 

Green chutney
Ingredients:
MINT | पुदीना 1 CUP
FRESH CORIANDER | हरा धनिया 1 CUP
GINGER | अदरक 1 INCH
GREEN 
CHILLI | हरी मिर्च 2 NOS. 
SALT | नमक TO TASTE
DRY MANGO POWDER | आमचूर पाउडर 1 TBSP
BLACK SALT | काला नमक ½ TSP
CUMIN POWDER | जीरा पाउडर ½ TSP
ICE CUBE | बर्फ 
WATER | पानी AS REQUIRED 
Method:
In a mixer jar add all the ingredients of the chutney & grind it into a fine paste, your green chutney is ready.
Amchur Chutney
Ingredients:
DRY MANGO POWDER | आमचूर पाउडर 75 GRAMS
WATER | पानी 750 ML (ADDED GRADUALLY)
JAGGERY | गुड़ 500 GRAMS
SALT | नमक TO TASTE
BLACK SALT | काला नमक 1 TSP
ROASTED CUMIN POWDER | भुने जीरे का पाउडर 1 TBSP
GINGER POWDER | सोंठ 1 TSP
BLACK PEPPER POWDER | काली मिर्च का पाउडर ¼ TSP
FENNEL POWDER | सौंफ का पाउडर ¼ TSP
KASHMIRI RED CHILLI POWDER | कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च पाउडर 1 TBSP
Method:
In a stock pot add the dry mango powder & gradually add the water while mixing it continuously to form a lump free mixture. 
Then add all the remaining ingredients & switch on the flame.
Stir well & cook over high flame until the jaggery melts & bring the chutney to a boil. 
Further lower the flame to medium & let it simmer for 15 mins.
Switch off the flame & let it cool down completely.
Amchur ki chutney is ready, you can store it in the fridge for a few months & freeze it to store it for a year.

#YFL #SanjyotKeer #tikkichole

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 25 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nestlé Nangrow - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 21st August 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Kaffara Digitally Presented by Nestlé Nangrow

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: 5 Crazy Hotels of Japan! 🤯 | Solo in Japan 🇯🇵
snippet.description:
#japan 
⭐️ Headout is the best app out there to have amazing experience internationally! 
⭐️Get upto get ₹2000 off on your first booking with Headout : 
https://bit.ly/4dLJJb6 - Allstar Food Tour in Tokyo
https://bit.ly/3XcRul2 - All Headout experiences in Tokyo


==============================================================

⭐️ Order Melodies of India (book) : https://melodiesofindia.com/
⭐️Join our Storytelling MasterClass for Youtube : https://monkeymagic.wtf/

==============================================================

TimeStamps :
0:00 - Introduction 
2:10 - Hello from Japan 
2:57 - Capsule Hotel (oldest in Japan)
7:37 - Ryokan (traditional Hotel)
10:35 - crazy good experience 
12:15 - Internet Cafe 
15:07 - Weird but..okay 
16:18 - ❤️❤️❤️
16:50 - Robot Hotel 
17:45 - Love Hotel of Japan 

==============================================================
I’m going to Japan for a month!! 😭🥰🚀 

Like most of the people Japan has been a dream place to visit but i did not want to go just for 7-10days. I wanted to experience the land slowly and as wide as possible..and as luck would have it, my month long Visa was granted and today I’m heading to my first solo International Trip ever! 

Let’s see what next 51days has in store for us 🥰 
No Plan, Japan! 🇯🇵 

#travel #japantravel
